#: ui/antergos-welcome.glade:55
msgid "Welcome to Antergos NeXT!"
msgstr "Selamat Datang di Antergos NeXT!"

#: ui/antergos-welcome.glade:71
msgid ""
"Thank you for joining our community!\n"
"\n"
"We, the Antergos NeXT Developers, hope that you will enjoy using Antergos NeXT as much as we enjoy building it. The links below will help you get started with your new operating system. So enjoy the experience, and don't hesitate to send us your feedback."
msgstr ""
"Terimakasih telah bergabung di komunitas kami!\n"
"\n"
"Kami, pengembang Antergos NeXT berharap Anda dapat menikmati Antergos NeXT sebagaimana kami menikmati dalam membuatnya. Link dibawah ini akan membantu Anda untuk memulai mengggunakan sistem operasi baru Anda. Jadi nikmatilah semua pengalaman yang akan Anda alami dan jangan segan-segan untuk memberikan feedback kepada kami."

